'''网络驱动程序接口规范'''（Network Driver Interface Specification，缩写为NDIS）是微軟所提供的[[網路介面卡|網路介面卡]]（NIC）API，使網路介面卡和多個協議進行通信成為可能，功能相當於OSI資料鏈結層的[[邏輯鏈路控制|邏輯鏈路控制]]（LLC）。

NDIS 的版本演進如下<ref>{{Cite web|title=Overview of NDIS versions - Windows drivers|url=https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/network/overview-of-ndis-versions|accessdate=2020-03-24|work=docs.microsoft.com|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227131353/https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/network/overview-of-ndis-versions|dead-url=no}}</ref>：

* NDIS 2.0: [[MS-DOS|MS-DOS]], [[Windows_3.1x|Windows for Workgroups 3.1]], [[OS/2|OS/2]]
* NDIS 3.0: Windows for Workgroups 3.11, [[Windows_NT_3.5|NT 3.5]]
* NDIS 3.1: [[Windows_95|Windows 95]]
* NDIS 4.0: Windows 95 OSR2, [[Windows_NT_4.0|NT 4.0]]
* NDIS 4.1: [[Windows_98|Windows 98]], NT 4.0 SP3
* NDIS 5.0: [[Windows_98_SE|Windows 98 SE]], [[Windows_Me|Me]], [[Windows_2000|2000]]
* NDIS 5.1: [[Windows_XP|Windows XP]], [[Windows_Server_2003|Server 2003]]
* NDIS 5.2: Windows Server 2003 SP2
* NDIS 6.0: [[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]
* NDIS 6.1: Windows Vista SP1, [[Windows_Server_2008|Server 2008]]
* NDIS 6.20: [[Windows_7|Windows 7]], [[Windows_Server_2008_R2|Server 2008 R2]]
* NDIS 6.30: [[Windows_8|Windows 8]], [[Windows_Server_2012|Server 2012]]
* NDIS 6.40: [[Windows_8.1|Windows 8.1]], [[Windows_Server_2012_R2|Server 2012 R2]]
* NDIS 6.50: [[Windows_10|Windows 10]] 1507
* NDIS 6.51: Windows 10 1511
* NDIS 6.60: [[Windows_Server_2016|Windows Server 2016]], Windows 10 1607
* NDIS 6.70: Windows 10 1703
* NDIS 6.80: Windows 10 1709
* NDIS 6.81: Windows 10 1803
* NDIS 6.82: Windows 10 1809
* NDIS 6.83: Windows 10 1903

